'''Abdullah Mohammed Al-Khaibari''' ({{langx|ar|عبد الله محمد الخيبري}}, born 15 August 1996) is a Saudi Arabian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]] and [[Saudi Pro League]] club [[Al Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slstat.com/spl2016-2017ar/player.php?id=1805|title=إحصائيات رابطة دوري المحترفين السعودي 2016/2017 - عبد الله الخيبري}}</ref>

In May 2018, he was named in Saudi Arabia's preliminary [[Saudi Arabia national football team|squad]] for the [[2018 World Cup]] in [[Russia]].<ref>{{cite web|title= World Cup 2018: All the confirmed squads for this summer's finals in Russia|url= https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/440833652018}}{{dead link|date=September 2025|bot=medic}}{{cbignore|bot=medic}}</ref>

